---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../components/ui/Card.astro';
import Badge from '../components/ui/Badge.astro';
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';

const allNews = await getCollection('news');
const latestNews = allNews
  .sort((a, b) => new Date(b.data.pubDate).getTime() - new Date(a.data.pubDate).getTime())
  .slice(0, 8);
---

<Layout title="News | Manga Anime Webtoon" description="Latest announcements and release date updates for anime, manga, and webtoons.">
  <section class="w-full bg-canvas py-section px-lg">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto flex flex-col gap-xl">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-sm">
        <p class="font-mono text-caption uppercase tracking-wider text-mute">News</p>
        <h1 class="text-display-lg font-semibold tracking-[-1.28px] text-ink">New anime release dates and announcements</h1>
        <p class="text-body-lg text-body max-w-[720px]">Stay up to date with the latest release schedules, studio announcements, and upcoming anime premieres.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-lg">
        <ul class="space-y-md">
          <li>
            <h3 class="text-display-sm font-semibold text-ink">Kagurabachi</h3>
            <p class="text-body-sm text-body text-mute">Global anime release planned for Spring 2027, with preview screenings beginning in 2026.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h3 class="text-display-sm text-ink font-semibold">Ghost in the Shell</h3>
            <p class="text-body-sm text-body text-mute">New adaptation by Science SARU premieres July 7, 2026.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h3 class="text-display-sm text-ink font-semibold">JoJo's Bizarre Adventure: Steel Ball Run</h3>
            <p class="text-body-sm text-body text-mute">One of the most anticipated upcoming anime adaptations, scheduled for 2026.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h3 class="text-display-sm text-ink font-semibold">Black Torch</h3>
            <p class="text-body-sm text-body text-mute">Premieres July 4, 2026 on Crunchyroll.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h3 class="text-display-sm text-ink font-semibold">The Apothecary Diaries Season 3</h3>
            <p class="text-body-sm text-body text-mute">First cour arrives October 2026, with a movie and additional content planned afterward.</p>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <article class="rounded-3xl border border-divider bg-canvas-soft p-lg">
          <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold text-ink">Latest Anime Industry Updates</h2>
          <p class="text-body text-body">The anime industry continues to deliver exciting announcements for fans around the world. One of the biggest recent highlights is the return of <strong>Dorohedoro</strong>, with Season 2 unveiling a new ending-theme music video that offers another glimpse into the series' dark and chaotic world.</p>
          <p class="text-body text-body">Crunchyroll has also revealed its plans for <strong>Anime Expo 2026</strong>, including special panels, premieres, and exclusive events. The convention is expected to feature announcements for several upcoming anime projects and provide fans with early looks at highly anticipated releases.</p>
          <p class="text-body text-body">Meanwhile, anticipation continues to build around <strong>MAPPA's anniversary celebrations</strong>. Fans are hoping for major updates regarding popular franchises such as <em>Jujutsu Kaisen</em> and <em>Chainsaw Man</em>, along with announcements about future projects from the renowned animation studio.</p>
          <p class="text-body text-body">Looking ahead, the Summer anime season is shaping up to be one of the year's busiest periods. Streaming platforms and production studios are gradually revealing new trailers, key visuals, and release information for upcoming titles.</p>
          <p class="text-body text-body">The industry is also continuing discussions around artificial intelligence in animation. While technological tools are becoming more common across entertainment industries, anime creators and industry leaders have emphasized the importance of preserving human creativity at the heart of anime production.</p>
          <p class="text-body text-body">With new announcements arriving almost every week, anime fans have plenty to look forward to in the months ahead.</p>
          <p class="text-body text-body"><strong>Source:</strong> <a href="https://www.crunchyroll.com/news/latest" class="text-link hover:underline">https://www.crunchyroll.com/news/latest</a></p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
